==English==
===Noun===
'''protozoan''' (''pl.'' '''[[protozoa]]''')
#{{cytology}} any of the diverse group of [[eukaryote]]s, of the [[kingdom]] [[Protista]], that are primarily [[unicellular]], existing singly or aggregating into colonies, are usually [[nonphotosynthetic]], and are often classified further into [[phyla]] according to their [[capacity]] for and means of [[motility]], as by [[pseudopod]]s, [[flagella]], or [[cilia]].

===Adjective===
'''protozoan'''
#of, pertaining to, or characteristic of a [[protozoan]].

